  "title": "BAKER. TRAINEE BAKER",
  "description": "<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<p>Job Scope:</p>\n<p>• Able to produce bread/buns on schedule</p>\n<p>• Assist in preparations of bread and other items</p>\n<p>• Follows proper handling and right temperature of all food products</p>\n<p>• Monitoring, checking, and receiving stocks for baking ingredients</p>\n<p>• Responsible to maintain the premises of the baking area in a neat and hygienic manner</p>\n<p>• Practice good housekeeping &amp; workplace/kitchen safety awareness</p>\n<p>• Ensure compliance of all food safety standards in bakery functions</p>\n<p>• Assist in ad hoc duties as and when required</p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>• Prefer a minimum of 1-2 years and above of bakery work experience</p>\n<p>• Physical fit and able to carry heavy stuff</p>\n<p>• Ability to read and follow recipes</p>\n<p>• Possess baking skills</p>\n<p>• Good organizational skills</p>\n<p>• Must be able to adhere to health and safety regulations</p>\n<p>• Ability to meet strict deadlines</p>\n<p>Salary is negotiable subject to your work experiences!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>FULL &amp; PART TIME POSITIONS AVAILABLE</p>\n<p>Min 4days . $12.50/hr </p>",
